			<diagram xmi:id="EAID_1C264E1A_10CD_4b0e_9565_9890D5B54547">
				<model package="EAPK_1ACEFA57_4ABB_4d99_90F3_D1320B5B2970" localID="5" owner="EAPK_1ACEFA57_4ABB_4d99_90F3_D1320B5B2970"/>
				<properties name="WMDR2-core" type="Logical" documentation="wmdr2-core&#xA;Notes&#xA;1. temporalExtent shall be realized as time:interval&#xA;2. temporal&amp;lt;Name&amp;gt; elements other than temporalGeometry shall be realized as arrays of dictionary objects for (begin) date, and the values of &amp;lt;Name&amp;gt;, e.g., &#xA;temporalTerritory = [{&#xA;&quot;date&quot;: &quot;2000-01-01&quot;,&#xA;&quot;territory&quot;: &quot;&amp;lt;ISO1&amp;gt;&quot;&#xA;},&#xA;{&#xA;&quot;date&quot; 2024-07-13&quot;, &#xA;&quot;territory&quot;: &quot;&amp;lt;ISO2&amp;gt;&quot;&#xA;}.&#xA;3. Following the OGC Features model, geometry = geolocation = coordinates + elevation&#xA;4. Schedules&#xA;&#xA;v0.1.4 Introduce instrument class.&#xA;v0.1.5 Expand instrument class.&#xA;v0.1.6 introduce more elements&#xA;v0.1.8 &#xA;   - require and expanded observation.observedDomain (includes domain, domainFeature [0..1], featureName [0..1])&#xA;   - introduce temporalGeometry.methods&#xA;v0.1.9&#xA;   - introduce deployment.temporalGeometry [0..1], verticalDistanceFromReferenceSurface [0..1]&#xA;   - rename localReferenceSurface to referenceSurface&#xA;   - rename observation.observedVariable to observation.observedProperty &#xA;   - remove xType suffix to manage expectations: many elements are 'Types', i.e., codelist-based&#xA;v0.1.10&#xA;   - rename environment.temporalTopographyBathymetry to topographyBathymetry&#xA;   - add environment.temporalSurfaceRoughness&#xA;   - rename instrumentCapability to instrument&#xA;   - rename instrumet.observableVariable to observedProperty, observableGeometry to observedGeometry."/>
				<project author="jkl" version="0.1.10" created="2026-03-06 10:35:24" modified="2026-06-13 10:24:00"/>
